#define ll long long
#define sc(n) scanf("%d",&n)
#define scl(n) scanf("%lld",&n)
#define prt(n) printf("%d\n",n)
using namespace std;
bool arr[1000001];
int main()
{
	int t;
	ll n;
	//freopen("in.txt","r",stdin);
	sc(t);

	{
		scl(n);

			prt(i);
			arr[i]=1;
		}
			
	}
return 0;
}
